:01.000Z","msg":"藍到發黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e857f4ef736f7ee2a9a6951d3abea5f59728df8","tid":2363640,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b93bb37eed6ea88289f410857cf6b7601836e9","tid":2363640,"uid":121146,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"我第一次聽冇權既人被威迫   可以屈成納粹  <br />\n美豬到底係智障定壞腦？ <br />\nbtw e d垃圾言論對香港人黎講一d都唔新鮮  因為港共日撚日講"},{"pid":"abb23abf195e4950ad3c511e9c3e12f4d27712bf","tid":2363640,"uid":72795,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"Well said<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3df40b659a6518395de608d5810d2bf5c30bd13","tid":2363640,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3c4765a3a15fd28e782e7c317e9351ce0107fc","tid":2363640,"uid":336429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49037c136bb1b5062d8c7c7a503b2b782e8f0ca7","tid":2363640,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"在美國國會發生暴力攻擊事件後，好萊塢巨星、同時也是前加州州長阿諾史瓦辛格(Arnold Schwarzenegger)，10日形容這是美國總統川普的未遂政變，還拿來和納粹德國相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n在一支迅速瘋傳的推特影片中，這位昔日的動作片巨星將川普支持者的攻擊行動，和「碎玻璃屠殺」事件(Kristallnacht，the Night of Broken Glass)相比擬。<br />\n<br />\n這是指1938年11月9日至10日凌晨，納粹黨員與黨衛隊襲擊德國全境的猶太人事件，包括砸碎猶太商家的窗戶，這被認為是對猶太人有組織屠殺的開始。<br />\n<br />\n影片中的阿諾史瓦辛格坐在書桌前，兩旁是美國國旗和加州州旗，他沈重的表示，6日是發生在美國的碎玻璃屠殺日，碎玻璃就是國會的窗戶。<br />\n<br />\n1947年出生於奧地利的阿諾史瓦辛格說，他的身邊曾經圍繞著沮喪的人們，靠著喝酒來逃避他們參與這個史上最邪